Parliament, Wednesday, 13 March 2019 – The joint meeting of the Standing and Select Committees on Appropriations to conduct public hearings on the 2019 Public Audit Excess Bill [B7 - 2019] that was scheduled for today has been cancelled. ISSUED BY PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSONS OF THE STANDING AND SELECT COMMITTEES ON APPROPRIATIONS, MS YVONNE PHOSA AND MR CHAREL DE BEER. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairpersons, please contact: Name: Felicia Lombard
